==Spanish==

===Suffix===
'''-ico''' ''m'' '''-ica''' ''f''

# [[-ic]]
# usually derogative diminutive suffix

===Usage note===
In definition 1, the emphasis will fall on the sylable before the suffix (e.g. ''[[cuántico]]'', with emphasis on /a/).  For definition 2, emphasis falls on the first sylable of the suffix (e.g. ''[[marica]]'', with emphasis on /i/).

